{"tid":1412200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今晚係關鍵] 擺工係一個滾雪球遊戲","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:13:59.000Z","uid":243928,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"92d8ac2c8ab8954f67923d27242922d17be936be","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"擺工唔會係一、兩日的事，而係一個中長期的鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n而家香港大概可以分為三派打工仔<br />\n<br />\n1. 主動擺工，無包袱，更加會幫人擺工，只有一至兩成的後生仔敢玩。<br />\n<br />\n2. 心想擺工，有包袱，怕比人秋後算賬，但如果有合適的籍口，就會配合擺工，呢班人起碼總人數一半。<br />\n<br />\n3. 返工藍絲魔人，不論包袱，只撐政府，熱愛工作，十號風球都要返工的人，呢班廢工，表面係無藥可救，但都係人，當個個都唔返，佢地重係咪有呢個動力，迫自己返工呢？同樣地，都係有一至兩成。<br />\n<br />\n其實今日對廣大市民，不論藍黃都有一個極大的心理影響，重點令到種類2, 3的打工仔了解到，其實真係有可能擺工。<br />\n<br />\n今日得你一個唔返，你又出左去幫手塞地鐵搵到有兩個市民返唔到工。<br />\n<br />\n聽日原本種類2的人出埋黎，一齊塞，令到多幾個人返唔到工。<br />\n<br />\n今日一個唔返工。<br />\n<br />\n聽日三個唔返工。<br />\n<br />\n後日五個唔返工。<br />\n<br />\n直到全間公司無人返工，而老闆亦都無法秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n擺工係一場運動，更重要係可持續性的運動。綜觀外國如美國、法國等地，一場成功的擺工工潮，係至少維持一星期，甚至數已月計的運動。雪球效應，越滾越大，直至蔓延至公務員，直至政府無法負擔得起後果，終會跪低。<br />\n<br />\n所以今日擺左工的人，聽日要繼續擺，因為今日心思思想擺工的人，聽朝見到新聞，全部塞死曬，自然有人出黎幫拖，日復日，一場成工的擺工工潮正式展開。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"d97e8cc543b47b329d76f73e9851d2879f4cde2b","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:46:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cb03f719cb1692f1884caaf85b5f42003aa77bd","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2824abfee115a2ad518ebe9cae35f295ca7e2e10","tid":1412200,"uid":34217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"好難，但點都要試"},{"pid":"458df8eea2eda1d85fecb8e452ffcb682ac37445","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26f85dc8904ccee1ccbadb7d4b609cd2ee39ab41","tid":1412200,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416ee87bff829a74d8a5fe7effd9c00b4071470e","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2824abfee115a2ad518ebe9cae35f295ca7e2e10","tid":1412200,"uid":34217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"好難，但點都要試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"塞多一日，真係塞多一日，不論海陸空，要而家開始推。擺多一日就有迴響。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7154de1c4d2660d3a10aba4f31ab878d5ce0fb","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"046ed7983d710e79e5783b81d6522b6c9c25758a","tid":1412200,"uid":114537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"擺你老母"},{"pid":"3c65d1794af9c6841e387881ed00bf09ef818493","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:55:09.000Z","msg":"堅持多一日，就會愈來愈多人加入，開始係青年，之後到中年，分分鐘廢老都頂唔緊，要加入擺工，講真，邊個鍾意返工，佢地只係唔敢唔返。無地鐵，交通擠塞，甚至係朝早已經開大拖，放緊tg ，全部都係極好的籍口唔返工。"},{"pid":"07013c5050babed7195d877d8f88304deedc71ab","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:57:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10d30fcec2237d14416cf5adcf388fbbdd648e3a","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:58:30.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"6ddba097f8aff41d4afa00ca4e328435b11be9ed","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bbaef86b336d151db1655bb204d5d99e00d9230","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9883947c69f0986183b6d42faccdde0be06baee2","tid":1412200,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf2b10959225950c82592e56fe4ae124fd10577","tid":1412200,"uid":292131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"罷"},{"pid":"e5696d9c9d8033132cc8502e26b09ab7e45ec17b","tid":1412200,"uid":243928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"同埋點解今晚係關鍵呢？就係今晚必須開大拖，每日幫市民集氣，試想像下六點鐘放工時間龍翔道放緊催淚彈，而一眾打工仔因為警察所以返唔到屋企，佢地會點諗呢？"},{"pid":"482c8850a4e4e4d5d166401186cb5fd321f8983e","tid":1412200,"uid":289741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n係罷啊！擺咩啊！"},{"pid":"50a011545a66d0a41a4359a36195fbf96456e016","tid":1412200,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1a1ea90232aa8930d6f2d82e36955d3a932e934","tid":1412200,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"罷呀"},{"pid":"4afd0590e62c3ce94d4b326ea71313520514e4bb","tid":1412200,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}